Thin Helm wrapper. Inherits demo-friendly defaults from this module; expose your own values via `var.values`.

## Usage

```hcl
module "{{NAME}}" {
  source = "git::https://github.com/<org>/traefik-demo.git//{{SECTION}}/{{PLATFORM}}/{{NAME}}?ref=vX.Y.Z"

  # Defaults are dev-grade. Override only what you need.
  values = {
    # see chart docs for available keys
  }
}
```

## Notes

- Requires the `helm` and `kubernetes` providers already configured against the target cluster (see `compute/<cloud>/<cluster>` outputs).
- This module has no outputs by default — the Helm provider exposes status via `helm_release.this.status`. Add module outputs if downstream demos need to reach into the install.

